Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:04.75,Lyrics1cz,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}a tvá postava se ztratila v dálce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:07.05,Lyrics1cz,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(0,250)}Budu si to pamatovat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:09.17,Lyrics1cz,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}nehledě na změny.
